events.description: A 30-minute meeting regarding Jeffrey Epstein was scheduled for 10:00 PM to 10:30 PM UTC. The calendar entry is marked as personal and high priority.

keyFacts: A meeting specifically regarding Jeffrey Epstein was scheduled for January 18, 2019.
The meeting was marked as 'PERSONAL' and given a high priority level of 5.
The meeting was scheduled for a 30-minute duration in the evening (22:00-22:30 UTC).
The calendar entry was created and modified on the same day, January 18, 2019.
This meeting occurred in early 2019, a period of renewed investigation and shortly before Epstein's arrest in July 2019.
